DRONE SAFETY REMINDER:

- Always maintain visual line of sight with your drone
- Check weather conditions before flight
- Ensure adequate battery levels and GPS signal strength  
- Respect no-fly zones and airspace restrictions
- Follow manufacturer safety guidelines
- Never fly over people or private property without permission
